## Anti-patterns to avoid
- N+1 / unbounded queries — page or batch.
- Blocking the main thread with I/O or heavy compute.
- Rebuilding large subtrees on every state change.
- Loading full datasets when a count/window suffices.

## Rules
- A change to a budgeted path must not regress its budget; note the measurement in the report.
